    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the orzo is almost cooked, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>remaining basil butter</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min</p><p>Drain, then add your <strong>king prawns</strong> and <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through – these are your <strong>garlicky king prawns</strong></p>",
